projects.description:
Antoon Blokland supports WaterWorX in the execution of the investment strategy.
1. Assesses DFI’s and Impact investors on their ability to finance investments in drinking water projects, and develop cooperation arrangements with WaterWorX;
2. Support project managers to prepare and develop investment projects from the WaterWorX programme;
3. Monitor the progress of the investments in achieving the roadmap to meet the 10 m people by 2030, and advise WaterWorX on interventions around this;
4. Advise WaterWorX on the enabling environment and conducive policies of investments in wa-ter;
